column5: Washer/Dryer! Wireless internet. Walk to Dell Children's Hospital. Close to I35 & Hyde Park, near by excellent restaurants, vintage shopping, coffee shops, bookstores, bars. Air-conditioned Accommodations--1 Queen bed, 1 day bed, also a twin-size fold-out couch-bed. Licensed by the city. Complimentary Coffee/Shampoo. Full Kitchen. Toaster/Microwave.
